Who in their right mind

00:16:48.560 --> 00:16:49.360
would stay awake at this hour?

00:16:49.360 --> 00:16:51.160
No, these two officers

00:16:51.160 --> 00:16:53.440
came to ask about Wang Xichuan and his son.

00:16:53.440 --> 00:16:53.960
Oh.

00:16:55.320 --> 00:16:56.840
Hello, officers.

00:16:57.160 --> 00:16:59.160
What happened to Wang Xichuan and his son?

00:16:59.160 --> 00:17:00.120
Did they commit a crime?

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:00.840
He's dead.

00:17:00.960 --> 00:17:03.040
The body parts in the crop fields were his.

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:03.720
Dead?

00:17:03.840 --> 00:17:04.280
Yes.

00:17:05.160 --> 00:17:07.520
I heard Wang Xichuan has a son named Wang Mingming.

00:17:07.520 --> 00:17:09.079
He worked for you, right?

00:17:09.440 --> 00:17:10.720
Oh, yes, he did.

00:17:11.240 --> 00:17:12.040
Tell you what,

00:17:12.119 --> 00:17:13.480
come with me to the village office

00:17:13.480 --> 00:17:15.640
and tell us about Wang Xichuan and his son.

00:17:15.640 --> 00:17:17.640
Oh, okay.

00:17:17.839 --> 00:17:19.720
Right now?

00:17:19.760 --> 00:17:20.319
Now.

00:17:20.319 --> 00:17:21.319
Oh, now.

00:17:33.760 --> 00:17:37.040
Thank the gods for granting this holy water.

00:17:51.640 --> 00:17:53.720
Drink this bowl of holy water.

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:56.720
It guarantees a long life

00:17:56.720 --> 00:18:00.040
and good fortune. Hahaha!

00:18:07.560 --> 00:18:08.360
Drink.

00:18:16.880 --> 00:18:17.640
Oh my.

00:18:18.200 --> 00:18:21.560
This girl has long hair

00:18:22.320 --> 00:18:24.320
and a face full of scars.